# Hostel Room Allocation System

This project is a simple Java program that helps manage hostel room allocation for students.

## Features
- Add student details
- Allocate rooms
- Display student records

## Technologies Used
- Java
- Object Oriented Programming

## How to Run
1. Compile the program:
   javac HostelRoomAllocation.java

2. Run the program:
   java HostelRoomAllocation
